title: American Horror Story 8: TRAILER (Fan Made)
author: American Horror Story 10
comment: When it was announced that Jessica Lange was going to be returning whether it is for one or more episodes I screamed!!! THE QUEEN IS RETURNING
Everyone is screaming for Jessica, but... GUYS, EVERYTHING IS CONECTED AND NOW WE KNOOOW!!

WTF... she’s back and I’m just ready to see this season unfold in front of my very eyes LoL. 
Two of my favorite seasons
It's true, Jessica is returning as Constance Langdon
Ohh hell yea I’m gonna start watching again. WE LOVE YOU JESSICA
description:
Teaser Trailer - American Horror Story, Season 8.
Premieres Wednesday September 12th, 2018.
